{"tid":1473761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人地外國都做緊野啦,我地文宣都配合啦下，唔好要人白做。","createTime":"2019-08-15T02:53:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T03:12:54.000Z","uid":62011,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d37e54ae8ab405b3a0827f403d6b53e2954bdfe8","tid":1473761,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:53:33.000Z","msg":"大家都呢幾日睇到新聞見到外國已經聲討中共同港共，人地已經開始做野，我地都要跟隨配合下啦。你唔配合下，唔出聲人地以為等運到，都唔知點幫你啊。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係外國巴絲可以做:</span></strong><br />\n1<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>. 展開國際遊說</strong></span>，向美國的議員說明香港的人權情況。目前俄羅斯及北韓加入支援中國，合力在香港鎮壓民權運動，形成了<span style=\"color: red;\">邪惡軸心國</span>的結盟，足以令西方警覺，這次特朗普對中共的鬥爭，是延續上次二次大戰以來的東西陣營的冷戰。<br />\n<br />\n方法:<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">寫信去國會議員或者元</span></strong>首，說明香港面對既<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">人道問題同類似二次世界大戰既延續</span></strong>。請他們幫手做以下事情:<br />\nA. 按國際標準，提供政治庇護比有需要的人 (加拿大德國最有可能)<br />\nGrant asylum to some protesters in accordance with the Refugee Convention.<br />\n<br />\nB. 根據Global Magnitsky Act, 凍結違反人權的狗狗和所謂官員 (英美加都有類似法例)<br />\nFreeze the assets and deny entry of human rights violators in accordance with the Global Magnitsky Act.<br />\n<br />\nC. 派醫療船/ 類似無國界醫生的團隊。<br />\nSend their medical team/hospital ship to Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\nD. BNO 平權。<br />\nFor UK: grant more rights to BNO holders.<br />\n<br />\n2. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">和平集會及展覽。</span></strong> 今次外國出聲，唔多唔少因為黑驚暴力對待示威者。612. 721, 728, 811咁多暴力鎮壓事件，足夠做一次展覽(我唔係消費佢地ge犧牲)俾本地外國領事人員同外國人、本地人睇，打張人道牌，等人地好出聲介入。<br />\n<br />\n如果可以，可以<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">剪輯一套中英記錄片</span></strong>，紀錄6月到依家發生既事。唔好睇少呢部片，影音既宣傳力，震撼力好大。更重要既係，由頭到尾咁樣同外國人解釋香港發生咩事，好多外國人唔知道發生咩事，淨係知黑驚打人、政府逃避等等片面消息。對於我地，完整紀錄片可以點返起團火!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n<strong>紀錄片寫實為主、唔落任何戲劇因素、情感。</strong><br />\n呢到需要技術剪片、導演、編寫(中英文)、旁述配合，影視系學生最好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n參考:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h8H_alCdY8c&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;fbclid=IwAR1unQ2J6qSmwRAoL0AMhu23FJSIF_ctiH00SLqP4v_9pJbQpwNcRyQMhAg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dh8H_alCdY8c%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%26fbclid%3DIwAR1unQ2J6qSmwRAoL0AMhu23FJSIF_ctiH00SLqP4v_9pJbQpwNcRyQMhAg&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQegw2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=7cce2e32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h8H_alCdY8c&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;fbclid=IwAR1unQ2J6qSmwRAoL0AMhu23FJSIF_ctiH00SLqP4v_9pJbQpwNcRyQMhAg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Hvds2AIiWLA&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;fbclid=IwAR1fl6LSahCiP0uWhDpgTtrGQTHTXgMOTybEx7vzGFSSOyGiiwVCtqMtxzs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHvds2AIiWLA%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%26fbclid%3DIwAR1fl6LSahCiP0uWhDpgTtrGQTHTXgMOTybEx7vzGFSSOyGiiwVCtqMtxzs&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQegw2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=5c5d5e12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Hvds2AIiWLA&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;fbclid=IwAR1fl6LSahCiP0uWhDpgTtrGQTHTXgMOTybEx7vzGFSSOyGiiwVCtqMtxzs</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏本地資產階級</span></strong>。提醒佢地<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">逃犯引渡條例草案仍然刊登在《憲報》上，並無撤回，九月立法會復會之後，如果泛民或政府重提法案，佢地會被共產黨盤剝家產，侵吞股份，扔入監牢。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加油香港人，一定得架!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"204199db9c7a6739eb47929dd64111cd0954d31a","tid":1473761,"uid":268285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:01:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/1161774305895694336?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F1161774305895694336%3Fs%3D09&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQegw2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=3e8f5364\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDon